snippet.title: Hyrule Warriors - Boss Pack DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
The first trailer of the Hyrule Warriors Boss Pack DLC. This pack contains two new game modes; Boss Challenge and Ganon's Fury as well as a few new costumes.

The Boss Pack will be available to download from the Wii U eShop on March 12th, 2015

Check us out on twitter: https://twitter.com/LTNintendo
Web: http://www.letstalknintendo.com/
